BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/nil.html"] ="This small Sudanese Restau&shy;rant near Boxha&shy;gener Platz offers quite a few vegan options, e. g. falafel and Tofu Mada&shy;gas&shy;car Sand&shy;wich&quot;. The Fohl, Vegan and Bamiya plat&shy;ters, served with a great peanut sauce, combine a vari&shy;ety of tastes and are really deli&shy;cious.<br/><br/>Nil offers great food and great value for money. Vegan dishes are clearly marked on the menu. The non vegan dishes are a draw&shy;back of course. The staff is, however, well-​informed and happy to help.<br/><br/>";
