BVApp.models.Data["reviews/de/india-palace.html"] ="Direkt an der Hermann&shy;straße in Neukölln befin&shy;det sich der India Palace 2. Hier steht der Chef selber am Herd. Das Geschäft ist zwar nicht spezi&shy;ell vegan ausge&shy;wie&shy;sen, doch ist die Zube&shy;rei&shy;tung vega&shy;ner Spei&shy;sen für den freund&shy;li&shy;chen Inha&shy;ber nichts Unge&shy;wöhn&shy;li&shy;ches. Die Grund&shy;kom&shy;po&shy;nen&shy;ten aller Gerichte werden nach dessen Anga&shy;ben ohne&shy;hin ohne Zugabe tieri&shy;scher Ingre&shy;den&shy;zien zube&shy;rei&shy;tet. Diese werden in der Regel erst später hinzu&shy;ge&shy;ge&shy;ben.<br/><br/>Alle vege&shy;ta&shy;ri&shy;schen Gerichte können auch vegan zube&shy;rei&shy;tet werden, wenn es gewünscht wird.<br/><br/>Die Gerichte liegen zwischen 2 und 7,50 , sind also für ziem&shy;lich jeden erschwing&shy;lich. Zudem bietet die Loca&shy;tion einen Liefer&shy;ser&shy;vice mit einem Mindest&shy;be&shy;stell&shy;wert von 15  an.<br/><br/>";
BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/dolores-burritos.html"] ="This small restau&shy;rant is situ&shy;ated near Alexan&shy;der&shy;platz (square) at Rosa-​Luxem&shy;burg Straße 7. The dishes are as wild and loud as the music and the uncon&shy;ven&shy;tional décor. The restau&shy;rant special&shy;izes in Burri&shy;tos and, thanks to the grow&shy;ing trend towards the vegan diet, offers a vegan option as well. The vegan options are clearly marked.<br/><br/>The staff told us that they are very care&shy;ful to use only &quot;vegan&quot; kitchen appli&shy;ances and cutlery (e. g. deep fryers and knives) when prepar&shy;ing vegan dishes. If you would like, you can make sure of this your&shy;self as patrons can see the kitchen area and watch the staff prepare the food.<br/><br/>The staff is friendly, constantly scur&shy;ries around and seems to have every&shy;thing under control even though the restau&shy;rant occa&shy;sion&shy;ally has an air of chaos to it.<br/><br/>The reason&shy;able prices allow for a second burrito in case youre famished. The home&shy;made lemon&shy;ades are another special&shy;ity and if you have a sweet tooth, you will be happy to know that Dolores also offers vegan cakes from Freck&shy;les.<br/><br/>";
